summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., June 03, 2025--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial technology, today announced that ATLAS SP Partners (ATLAS), a leading provider of structured and asset-backed credit to institutional borrowers and institutional investors, has chosen FIS’ Commercial Loan Servicing solution to help power ATLAS’ loan lifecycle processing workflows.
